name: SKL
description:
For many people, skulls depict death and the concept of mortality, they are a stark reminder that life is fleeting and are seen as one of the most powerful symbols on this planet. 

Many other connotations can be drawn from a symbolic skull, especially in the art world. They can represent transformation and change, whilst also constitute thoughts of wealth, power, strength & protection.

The human brain assigns meaning to many objects and symbols to help our understanding of the reality around us.
